1. Introduction

The Heart Disease Analytics project was developed to analyze heart disease data using MySQL, Tableau, and Flask. Performance testing was conducted to evaluate the efficiency, responsiveness, and accuracy of the dashboard while handling the dataset.

2. Testing Environment
Component	Details
Database	MySQL
Visualization Tool	Tableau Public
Backend	Flask
Programming Language	Python
Dataset	Heart Disease UCI Dataset
Records	308
Attributes	15

3. Performance Evaluation
Test	Status
Dataset Import	Passed
SQL Queries Execution	Passed
Tableau Connection	Passed
Dashboard Loading	Passed
KPI Display	Passed
Charts Rendering	Passed
Interactive Filters	Passed
Web Integration	Passed

4. Dashboard Performance
Total Records Analyzed: 308
Total Visualizations: 10
KPI Cards: 4
Interactive Filters: 5
Dashboard Response: Smooth
Errors Encountered: None

5. Conclusion

The project successfully analyzed the Heart Disease dataset with good 
performance. SQL queries executed correctly, Tableau dashboards 
responded efficiently, and all visualizations were displayed without
 noticeable delay. The overall system met the expected performance 
 requirements.